owt-agent for OpenWrt
=====================

This package installs the `owt-agent` gateway execution daemon.

Installed files:
- `/usr/sbin/owt-agent`
- `/etc/init.d/owt-agent`
- `/etc/config/owt-agent` (service options)
- `/etc/owt-agent/config.ini` (agent connection config)
- `/etc/owt-agent/params.ini` (execution default parameters)
- `/var/log/owt-agent/owt-agent.log` (runtime log file, fallback: working dir `logs/`)

Quick start:
1. Enable and start:
   `/etc/init.d/owt-agent enable`
   `/etc/init.d/owt-agent start`
2. Check service:
   `logread -e owt-agent`
3. Verify process:
   `ps | grep owt-agent`

UCI service options (`/etc/config/owt-agent`):
- `enabled`: `1` or `0`
- `config_file`: runtime config path
- `respawn_threshold`, `respawn_timeout`, `respawn_retry`
